<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The 30-Minute Strength System | For Engineer Dads Who Refuse to Let Go</title>
    <meta name="description" content="A 12-week progressive strength program built for software engineers with infant twins, sleep deprivation, and zero time to waste.">
    
    <!-- Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Source+Sans+3:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-primary: #0a0a0a;
            --bg-secondary: #141414;
            --bg-card: #1a1a1a;
            --text-primary: #ffffff;
            --text-secondary: #a3a3a3;
            --text-muted: #737373;
            --accent: #f97316;
            --accent-hover: #fb923c;
            --accent-glow: rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.4);
            --border: #262626;
            --success: #22c55e;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Source Sans 3', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-primary);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Noise texture overlay */
        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
            opacity: 0.03;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 24px;
        }

        /* Header */
        header {
            padding: 24px 0;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--bg-primary) 0%, transparent 100%);
        }

        .header-inner {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .logo span {
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .nav-cta {
            background: transparent;
            border: 1px solid var(--accent);
            color: var(--accent);
            padding: 10px 24px;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .nav-cta:hover {
            background: var(--accent);
            color: var(--bg-primary);
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 120px 0 80px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            width: 60%;
            height: 100%;
            background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 30%, var(--accent-glow) 0%, transparent 60%);
            opacity: 0.3;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .hero-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 80px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .hero-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 8px 16px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            color: var(--accent);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out;
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
            font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5.5rem);
            line-height: 0.95;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out 0.1s both;
        }

        .hero-title span {
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            max-width: 480px;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out 0.2s both;
        }

        .hero-subtitle strong {
            color: var(--text-primary);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .hero-cta {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: var(--bg-primary);
            padding: 18px 36px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out 0.3s both;
        }

        .hero-cta:hover {
            background: var(--accent-hover);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px var(--accent-glow);
        }

        .hero-cta svg {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .hero-cta:hover svg {
            transform: translateX(4px);
        }

        .hero-visual {
            position: relative;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out 0.4s both;
        }

        .hero-image-placeholder {
            aspect-ratio: 4/5;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero-image-placeholder::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-glow) 0%, transparent 50%);
            opacity: 0.1;
        }

        .placeholder-icon {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .placeholder-text {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        }

        .hero-stats {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 24px;
            margin-top: 32px;
            padding-top: 32px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .stat {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-value {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--accent);
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        /* Problem Section */
        .problem {
            padding: 120px 0;
            background: var(--bg-secondary);
            position: relative;
        }

        .problem::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--border), transparent);
        }

        .section-label {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.2em;
            color: var(--accent);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 48px;
        }

        .problem-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 32px;
        }

        .problem-card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 32px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .problem-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent);
            transform: translateY(-4px);
        }

        .problem-icon {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            color: var(--accent);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .problem-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .problem-card p {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* Solution Section */
        .solution {
            padding: 120px 0;
        }

        .solution-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 80px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .solution-image-placeholder {
            aspect-ratio: 1;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .solution-content .section-title {
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .solution-description {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .solution-features {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .solution-features li {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 16px;
            padding: 16px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .solution-features li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .feature-check {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            background: var(--accent);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        .feature-check svg {
            width: 14px;
            height: 14px;
            color: var(--bg-primary);
        }

        .feature-text strong {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .feature-text span {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* What You Get Section */
        .includes {
            padding: 120px 0;
            background: var(--bg-secondary);
        }

        .includes-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 24px;
            margin-top: 48px;
        }

        .include-card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 40px;
            display: flex;
            gap: 24px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .include-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent);
        }

        .include-number {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: var(--accent);
            line-height: 1;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        .include-content h3 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .include-content p {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* Testimonial / Social Proof */
        .social-proof {
            padding: 120px 0;
        }

        .testimonial-card {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            position: relative;
        }

        .testimonial-card::before {
            content: '"';
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
            font-size: 12rem;
            color: var(--accent);
            opacity: 0.1;
            position: absolute;
            top: -20px;
            left: 40px;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .testimonial-text {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .testimonial-author {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .author-avatar {
            width: 56px;
            height: 56px;
            background: var(--bg-secondary);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .author-avatar svg {
            width: 28px;
            height: 28px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .author-info {
            text-align: left;
        }

        .author-name {
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .author-title {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }

        /* CTA Section */
        .cta {
            padding: 120px 0;
            background: var(--bg-secondary);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .cta::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            width: 800px;
            height: 800px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--accent-glow) 0%, transparent 70%);
            opacity: 0.15;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .cta-content {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .cta .section-title {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .cta-subtitle {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .signup-form {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            max-width: 480px;
            margin: 0 auto 24px;
        }

        .signup-form input {
            flex: 1;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 18px 24px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            font-family: inherit;
            transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .signup-form input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--accent);
        }

        .signup-form input::placeholder {
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .signup-form button {
            background: var(--accent);
            border: none;
            color: var(--bg-primary);
            padding: 18px 32px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .signup-form button:hover {
            background: var(--accent-hover);
        }

        .form-note {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }

        .success-message {
            display: none;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--success);
            padding: 24px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 480px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .success-message.show {
            display: block;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.4s ease-out;
        }

        .success-message h3 {
            color: var(--success);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        /* About Section */
        .about {
            padding: 120px 0;
        }

        .about-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 300px 1fr;
            gap: 60px;
            align-items: start;
        }

        .about-image-placeholder {
            aspect-ratio: 1;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .about-content .section-title {
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .about-text {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 1.0625rem;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .about-text strong {
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .about-credentials {
            display: flex;
            gap: 32px;
            margin-top: 32px;
            padding-top: 32px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .credential {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .credential svg {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .credential span {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            padding: 40px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .footer-inner {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .footer-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .footer-links a {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .footer-links a:hover {
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .footer-copy {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        /* Mobile Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .hero-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 48px;
            }

            .hero-visual {
                order: -1;
            }

            .hero-image-placeholder {
                aspect-ratio: 16/9;
                max-height: 400px;
            }

            .problem-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .solution-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 48px;
            }

            .solution-image-placeholder {
                order: -1;
                aspect-ratio: 16/9;
            }

            .includes-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .about-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 40px;
            }

            .about-image-placeholder {
                max-width: 300px;
                margin: 0 auto;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .header-inner {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 16px;
            }

            .hero {
                padding: 100px 0 60px;
            }

            .hero-stats {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 16px;
            }

            .signup-form {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .signup-form button {
                width: 100%;
            }

            .testimonial-card {
                padding: 40px 24px;
            }

            .testimonial-text {
                font-size: 1.25rem;
            }

            .about-credentials {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 16px;
            }

            .footer-inner {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 16px;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header-inner">
                <a href="#" class="logo">DEV<span>DAD</span></a>
                <a href="#signup" class="nav-cta">Join Waitlist</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-grid">
                <div class="hero-content">
                    <div class="hero-badge">For Engineer Dads Only</div>
                    <h1 class="hero-title">
                        The <span>30-Minute</span> Strength System
                    </h1>
                    <p class="hero-subtitle">
                        A 12-week progressive strength program built for software engineers with <strong>infant twins, sleep deprivation, and zero time to waste.</strong>
                    </p>
                    <a href="#signup" class="hero-cta">
                        Join the Waitlist
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-visual">
                    <div class="hero-image-placeholder">
                        <svg class="placeholder-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15.75l5.159-5.159a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l5.159 5.159m-1.5-1.5l1.409-1.409a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l2.909 2.909m-18 3.75h16.5a1.5 1.5 0 001.5-1.5V6a1.5 1.5 0 00-1.5-1.5H3.75A1.5 1.5 0 002.25 6v12a1.5 1.5 0 001.5 1.5zm10.5-11.25h.008v.008h-.008V8.25zm.375 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0z" />
                        </svg>
                        <span class="placeholder-text">Hero Image / Video</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hero-stats">
                        <div class="stat">
                            <div class="stat-value">30</div>
                            <div class="stat-label">Minutes Max</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat">
                            <div class="stat-value">12</div>
                            <div class="stat-label">Week Program</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat">
                            <div class="stat-value">3x</div>
                            <div class="stat-label">Per Week</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Problem Section -->
    <section class="problem">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-label">The Reality</div>
            <h2 class="section-title">You know the drill.</h2>
            <div class="problem-grid">
                <div class="problem-card">
                    <svg class="problem-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                    </svg>
                    <h3>Zero Time</h3>
                    <p>Between deployments, standups, and midnight feedings, your gym time evaporated. The 90-minute workouts you used to do? Not happening.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="problem-card">
                    <svg class="problem-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21.752 15.002A9.718 9.718 0 0118 15.75c-5.385 0-9.75-4.365-9.75-9.75 0-1.33.266-2.597.748-3.752A9.753 9.753 0 003 11.25C3 16.635 7.365 21 12.75 21a9.753 9.753 0 009.002-5.998z" />
